When trying to build the OMPI trunk or the 1.5 branch with clang-3.0, I cannot build VT.<div>If have tried both MacOS 10.7 and FreeBSD-9.0-RELEASE.</div><div>In all four builds (2 branches X 2 OSes) the failure appears to be &quot;deep&quot; in the C++ STL.</div>
<div><br></div><div>I strongly suspect that this is a Clang++ bug.</div><div>However, I am reporting it here in the hope that somebody more familiar with STL and/or the VT code can take a closer look to rule out the possibility that the STL *usage* might be &quot;border-line&quot;.</div>
